snippet.title: Kādomon: Hyper Auto Battlers – 1.0 Release Date Trailer | Launching April 7th
snippet.description:
LINKS
Steam - https://store.steampowered.com/app/2125540/Kdomon_Hyper_Auto_Battlers/
Twitter - https://x.com/KadomonGame
Discord - https://discord.com/invite/cXxTGMUdJf

Kādomon: Hyper Auto Battlers is launching into 1.0 on April 7th!
Get ready to collect, battle, and evolve over 230 mighty monsters in this fast-paced creature-collecting auto battler from indie studio Dino Rocket and publisher Fireshine Games.

With new content, powerful upgrades, and major gameplay improvements, there’s never been a better time to become the ultimate Kādomon trainer!
